-- flags {{{1
Flag dev
    Description:   Turn on development settings, like auto-reload templates.
    Default:       False

Flag merge
    Description:   Similar to dev, except with -Werror added.
    Default:       False

Flag library-only
    Description:   Build for use with "yesod devel"
    Default:       False

